---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="About" description="Floof is a fun, young, vibrant clothing brand from Southwest Florida.">
  <section class="border-b border-floof-dark/6 bg-floof-sand/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-14 md:py-20">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our story</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">
        About <span class="text-floof-pink">Floof</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-floof-dark/55">Where the Gulf breeze meets good vibes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 space-y-12">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">The short version</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-floof-dark/65 leading-relaxed">
        Floof started with a simple observation: Southwest Florida has a vibe unlike anywhere else, but most of the merch out there is generic palm tree prints. We wanted something different — clothes that capture the energy of living where the sun shines 250+ days a year.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-floof-dark">What&rsquo;s with the name?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-floof-dark/65 leading-relaxed">
        Floof is the sound a beach umbrella makes when the wind catches it. It&rsquo;s the feeling of sand between your toes. It&rsquo;s that perfect sunset moment when you think, &ldquo;Yeah, this is why I live here.&rdquo; Unserious by design.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-4">
      <a href="/store" class="btn btn--lg">Shop the collection</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
